"title": "1412: foreknowledge",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1412: foreknowledge",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Foreknowledge is an aspect of God's knowledge of everything, and thus nothing can surprise him. Jesus Christ had foreknowledge of his own death, resurrection and coming in glory.</p>\n<h2>God's foreknowledge</h2>\n<h3>Everything is within God's knowledge</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:9\">ISA 42:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:14\">1KI 22:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:28\">DAN 2:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:36\">MAT 24:36</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:32\">MRK 13:32</a></p>\n<h3>What God knows he ordains</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa46:10-Isa46:11\">ISA 46:10–46:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:23\">ACT 2:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:28-Rom8:30\">ROM 8:28–8:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:1-1Pet1:2\">1PE 1:1–1:2</a></p>\n<h3>God's foreknowledge of the Messiah</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:18\">ACT 3:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:1-Isa11:3\">ISA 11:1–11:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:7-Isa53:9\">ISA 53:7–53:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic5:2\">MIC 5:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:22-Acts2:23\">ACT 2:22–2:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:27-Acts4:28\">ACT 4:27–4:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:20\">1PE 1:20</a></p>\n<h2>God's foreknowledge and his election of his people</h2>\n<h3>God's sovereign choice</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:29\">ROM 8:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:4\">PRO 16:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:11-Rom9:12\">ROM 9:11–9:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:2\">ROM 11:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:4\">EPH 1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:1-1Pet1:2\">1PE 1:1–1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:20\">1PE 1:20</a></p>\n<h3>Human responsibility</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:3\">HEB 2:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:18\">JHN 3:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:36\">JHN 3:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:2\">1CO 15:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:1-2Cor6:2\">2CO 6:1–6:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:5-Eph5:6\">EPH 5:5–5:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:12\">HEB 3:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:4-Heb6:6\">HEB 6:4–6:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:1\">2PE 2:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:15\">HEB 3:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:7-Ps95:8\">PSA 95:7–95:8</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's foreknowledge</h2>\n<h3>Of events within his general ministry</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:64\">JHN 6:64</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:27\">MAT 17:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:31-Matt26:34\">MAT 26:31–26:34</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:27-Mark14:30\">MRK 14:27–14:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:34\">LUK 22:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:38\">JHN 13:38</a></p>\n<h3>Of his suffering and departure</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:1\">JHN 13:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:18\">MAT 26:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:31\">MRK 8:31</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:22\">LUK 9:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:50\">LUK 12:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:37\">LUK 22:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:14\">JHN 3:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:33\">JHN 7:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:11\">JHN 13:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:33\">JHN 13:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:28\">JHN 14:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:5\">JHN 17:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:4\">JHN 18:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:28\">JHN 19:28</a></p>\n<h3>Of his coming in glory and judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:27\">MAT 16:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:30-Matt24:31\">MAT 24:30–24:31</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:26-Mark13:27\">MRK 13:26–13:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:31\">MAT 25:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:38\">MRK 8:38</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:26\">LUK 9:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:26\">LUK 24:26</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's lack of knowledge of the timing of his coming in glory</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:32\">MRK 13:32</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:36\">MAT 24:36</a></p>",
